📍 Garden of Dreams, Goa
a little cafe that actually lives up to its name ✨

Let’s talk real:

🌿 Vibes? On-point. It’s like Pinterest threw up in the best way possible — boho cushions, dreamy plants, and zero rush energy.

🥗 Food? Surprisingly good. I came for the ambience, but the hummus made me stay. The smoothie bowl? Chef’s kiss.

🪴 Good for solo chilling or cute dates. Also perfect if you want to feel like the main character in a forest fairytale.

📸 Instagrammable corners? Every. Single. Inch. Warning: you’ll need extra storage.

📚 Bonus: They have books, quiet corners, and good playlists — basically therapy but with better lighting.

🧘‍♀️ I sat for 2 hours pretending to journal but actually just people-watched & ate banana bread.

🌼 If you’re in Goa & tired of loud beach clubs — this is your slow day paradise.

—

💬 Let me know if you’ve been here or want recos for more hidden gems like this.
Also yes, I did take 54 selfies and only posted few. Classic.

#GardenOfDreamsGoa #CafeVibes #GoaCafeHopping #KiranKhokharTravels #BohoVibes #HiddenGemGoa #MainCharacterMoments #kirankhokhar

📍 Garden of Dreams, Goa
a little cafe that actually lives up to its name ✨

Let’s talk real:

🌿 Vibes? On-point. It’s like Pinterest threw up in the best way possible — boho cushions, dreamy plants, and zero rush energy.

🥗 Food? Surprisingly good. I came for the ambience, but the hummus made me stay. The smoothie bowl? Chef’s kiss.

🪴 Good for solo chilling or cute dates. Also perfect if you want to feel like the main character in a forest fairytale.

📸 Instagrammable corners? Every. Single. Inch. Warning: you’ll need extra storage.

📚 Bonus: They have books, quiet corners, and good playlists — basically therapy but with better lighting.

🧘‍♀️ I sat for 2 hours pretending to journal but actually just people-watched & ate banana bread.

🌼 If you’re in Goa & tired of loud beach clubs — this is your slow day paradise.
